{"tid":294464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"故宮館事件 廉署終止調查","createTime":"2017-06-23T03:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T04:28:51.000Z","uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf91220e48c5a005d308b7e713d27aea8a3ee01","tid":294464,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】立法會議員毛孟靜於今年一月到廉政公署舉報，指候任特首林鄭月娥時任政務司司長時，忽然宣布興建西九故宮文化博物館的秘密協議，又偷步聘請建築師嚴迅奇擔任項目設計顧問，涉嫌公眾人員行為不當、私相授受，毛昨日接獲廉署回覆，指會終止有關調查。毛孟靜表示，三月接獲廉署通知會調查事件，直至昨日收到廉署的電話回覆，廉署認為事件沒有涉及公眾人員行為不當或私相授受等，指會終止調查。<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170623/00176_084.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170623%2F00176_084.html&d=J0RvhQqUFeYyBXbsm1e2ljPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5099a987\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170623/00176_084.html</a>"},{"pid":"794b9077183d1ba4013f0878846855a181d43d8b","tid":294464,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:40:02.000Z","msg":"一做特狗即刻冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎要等淋病完左任期先有望再查"},{"pid":"c49b2ba7ad27bde1c6c478ed53b6887c59d62849","tid":294464,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92258e1bd063112219dc593c89642eb2551e4e5f","tid":294464,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:01:55.000Z","msg":"其實可以執柒咗呢個部門，貪到咁明顯都可以話無事，算吧啦廉署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b73388ca9d52fb9be1b30736586f18c28391ec","tid":294464,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:08:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實可以執柒咗呢個部門，貪到咁明顯都可以話無事，算吧啦廉署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fu